Federico Castelluccio https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Federico_Castelluccio 0 Federico Castelluccio (born April 29, 1964) is an Italian-American actor and professional visual artist, who is known for his role as Furio Giunta on the HBO series, The Sopranos.
